Hollywood screen star Lupita Nyong&rsquo;o is showing that she doesn&#39;t only possess immense talent in acting but also in the rap game!The Queen of Katwe star, who is known for her acting prowess and stunning red carpet looks, just dropped a rap video dubbed Introducing My Alter Ego Troublemaker.The video was to celebrate her three million followers on social media platform Instagram.The Kenyan movie star shared the black-and-white video where she goes through her very long list of accomplishments and talents and gives a shout out to her Queen of Katwe co-star David Oyelowo.The rest of the 55-second-long video features more of her roles in film.She also raps about being a champion for elephants.Watch the video here.